Package: scFPCDE
Title: Functional PCA-Based Differential Expression for Single-Cell Trajectories
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ricardo J.", "Lopez Candelaria", 
                  email = "rlopez.research@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides methods to model, smooth, and test differential expression along pseudotime 
    using functional principal component analysis (FPCA). Includes FPCA fitting, permutation-based 
    tests, smoothing parameter tuning, and gene-level visualization functions for single-cell data.
